## Data License

Code in this repository (anything under `scripts/`, `pipeline/`, `docs/`, and
all `*.py` / `*.md` source files) is licensed under the MIT License above.

Data files under `dataset/questions/` are derived from the public APIs of
Polymarket, Kalshi, and Metaculus. Our curation, normalization, and
annotations are released under **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
International (CC BY 4.0)**. See `dataset/questions/DATASET_CARD.md` for
full attribution requirements and upstream source terms.

Downstream users are responsible for compliance with each upstream source's
Terms of Service when redistributing derivative works that incorporate the
underlying market data.
